	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you put a "delay next note by <em>n</em> frames within the row" effect in your music engine's bitstream (compare S3M effect SDx), you can get timing resolution almost as good as MIDI at the cost of some extra space.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


